videos.description: Jaevin Cumberland connects on a deep 3-pointer early for Cincinnati.
videos.headline: Cumberland drains deep 3

videos.description: Jaevin Cumberland throws the alley-oop up to Tre Scott who slams down a dunk at the delight of the crowd.

videos.headline: Cumberland's oop to Scott ignites the crowd

videos.description: Isaiah Maurice zips to the basket to coral the miss and throws down a two-handed jam.
